Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡進行面向最終決議的公正交涉..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對面送來了個不得了的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瑪利亞·托洛夫斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是女演員的兵器經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好一個超級美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔻蔻·海克梅迪亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有一位非常年輕可愛的經銷商小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直非常地在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.01,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.01,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們始終踱步於境界線之上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.73,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.73,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因此境風景獨好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.35,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eeny,meeny,miny,moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.35,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一，二，三，四...
